        "subject": "LU-11796 lov: Remove unnecessary assert",
        "message": "LU-11796 lov: Remove unnecessary assert\n\nThis is asserting on network data from the server, and\nadditionally, the LU-9846 (overstriping) work shows this\ncondition is not a problem if it does somehow occur.\n\nThis patch is intended only for the 2.10 and 2.12\nmaintenance branches.  It is expected to land to 2.13 as\npart of the overstriping feature.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I7b53eb63914f6e9d31a0747a40d09df9ffedaa91\n"
